{"tid":1878040,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【爆乳Pink Lady】泫雅情人節冧E'Dawn","createTime":"2020-02-13T11:07:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T11:08:29.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e9d1e0440ee1bfe6823b52a43736467a0763b48f","tid":1878040,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T11:07:21.000Z","msg":"出道13年的韓國27歲性感女歌手泫雅，去年9月高調認愛師弟E'Dawn後，不時放閃晒恩愛，泫雅人氣有增無減，工作源源不絕，頻獲邀到海外出席活動吸金。<br />\n<br />\n愛情事業雙贏的泫雅最近出任某內衣品牌的全球大使，蜜運中的她更顯自信，風騷大晒火辣身材!<br />\n<br />\n身穿粉紅色內衣的泫雅，化身爆乳Pink Lady，十分誘人!她又換上另一款黑色內衣瞓身露半股，而她示範的另一款玫瑰圖案內衣則最適合情人節，相信男友E'Dawn見到一定冧爆！"},{"pid":"a5c4eecc27e20ed4bb2b52ca09cc9e330e22706c","tid":1878040,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T11:07:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200213/photo/bkn-20200213075824074-0213_00862_001_01b.jpg?20200213104239\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200213%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200213075824074-0213_00862_001_01b.jpg%3F20200213104239&h=365b77dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2206ec97aa0c1116fcf7052aea6dfd1cca0c994a","tid":1878040,"uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T11:08:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/3c04afaf4a907dd0affe06e481d107ba/4285899bad9a22ab-a1/s500x750/c94c980a65d8d336118248b64b10268a08b4d208.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F3c04afaf4a907dd0affe06e481d107ba%2F4285899bad9a22ab-a1%2Fs500x750%2Fc94c980a65d8d336118248b64b10268a08b4d208.gifv&h=e068f076&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/5abacc1081a064f2d780e9659d10472f/4285899bad9a22ab-45/s500x750/5cfa3fabdf406e63017d781bc8ea5735157e6a60.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F5abacc1081a064f2d780e9659d10472f%2F4285899bad9a22ab-45%2Fs500x750%2F5cfa3fabdf406e63017d781bc8